{"tid":99342,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[實際應用]轉線有無必要擰頭望盲點？","createTime":"2017-01-29T06:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T14:09:40.000Z","uid":13558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7054a0a3ce2a473a1dea42d0ac468fbe3caad23f","tid":99342,"uid":13558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:37:50.000Z","msg":"今日老豆同我講側鏡虛線以外就望到盲點，<br />\n其實係咪真？ 有無車真係咁？ <br />\n講明先我部車無盲點輔助系統。<br />\n咁如果唔係，虛線以外其實有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n其次當年考車擰頭90度為求pass，<br />\n今日考完實際應用其實係咪無必要？<br />\nshoulder check是係咪過時更危險？<br />\n<br />\n事緣：<br />\n今年shoulder check畀人屌到傻話我危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左我認我擰頭移動到軚盤危險之外，<br />\n我覺得shoulder check無危險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n虛心求學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求各大佬指點迷津"},{"pid":"75d2827f71fb8e2c9059ce9a90b4517a538a736e","tid":99342,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:40:28.000Z","msg":"兩邊鏡唔使跟學車時教咁要見到3份1架車<br />\n我較到只睇到少少<br />\n<br />\ncut線時會望左邊<br />\n但cut右邊好少望<br />\n<br />\n揸開車就知係真係有盲點位完位睇唔到"},{"pid":"b8e95d31b73f50267deffe273387db12a7bc3d4e","tid":99342,"uid":11979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:40:45.000Z","msg":"Shoulder check唔望前面梗係危險啦 考試既野你以為有用？你會唔會捋豬腸呀學完車仲"},{"pid":"f731fea440b49abbaff23d157f53f4e862a01d00","tid":99342,"uid":26913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:42:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日老豆同我講側鏡虛線以外就望到盲點，<br />\n其實係咪真？ 有無車真係咁？ <br />\n講明先我部車無盲點輔助系統。<br />\n咁如果唔係，虛線以外其實有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n其次當年考車擰頭90度為求pass，<br />\n今日考完實際應用其實係咪無必要？<br />\nshoulder check是係咪過時更危險？<br />\n<br />\n事緣：<br />\n今年shoulder check畀人屌到傻話我危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左我認我擰頭移動到軚盤危險之外，<br />\n我覺得shoulder check無危險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n虛心求學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求各大佬指點迷津</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中過幾次伏，所以已訓練成必望盲點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n電單車、有時鬼掩眼，意外就發生"},{"pid":"3a05e047027e406aa1dfeed423f8d92dd59e63a9","tid":99342,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今日老豆同我講側鏡虛線以外就望到盲點，<br />\n其實係咪真？ 有無車真係咁？ <br />\n講明先我部車無盲點輔助系統。<br />\n咁如果唔係，虛線以外其實有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n其次當年考車擰頭90度為求pass，<br />\n今日考完實際應用其實係咪無必要？<br />\nshoulder check是係咪過時更危險？<br />\n<br />\n事緣：<br />\n今年shoulder check畀人屌到傻話我危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左我認我擰頭移動到軚盤危險之外，<br />\n我覺得shoulder check無危險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n虛心求學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求各大佬指點迷津</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中過幾次伏，所以已訓練成必望盲點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n電單車、有時鬼掩眼，意外就發生</blockquote><br />\n有時揸開明知無車<br />\n但習慣性都會望一望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97725d0941828f5eab7dc6d0e27e2858e6c263a","tid":99342,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:43:43.000Z","msg":"盲點輔助系統  低9能"},{"pid":"d3be4bd96a32b88a035a6f1eca8bc539d744c061","tid":99342,"uid":7754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:45:54.000Z","msg":"望盲點花你唔洗兩秒，點都望啦<br />\n細車好難睇架，到時出意外就大件事"},{"pid":"5e2cc84b332689c452eed9c68a7c52be68577c8f","tid":99342,"uid":26913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Shoulder check唔望前面梗係危險啦 考試既野你以為有用？你會唔會捋豬腸呀學完車仲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出路口一定睇，高速公路轉線睇埋中鏡其實都睇到"},{"pid":"ed7dc7348e8ed4c950c3de462ec41f7a2e0156a3","tid":99342,"uid":4032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:26:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2014/07/22/a1124670.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fxtr%2Fb5%2F2014%2F07%2F22%2Fa1124670.html&d=OECIOtpIYN%2BcfPKO8P2P33vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=c15e8180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2014/07/22/a1124670.html</a><br />\n<br />\n較好側鏡，shoulder check 都可以擰少啲同快啲。"},{"pid":"e14d410ffb324b00e1015b5e4efba7001da1073f","tid":99342,"uid":57774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:40:53.000Z","msg":"上高速公路一定睇 其餘就極少"},{"pid":"5736c4868f194510240716547ba7f77f04638856","tid":99342,"uid":28201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:44:27.000Z","msg":"啱啱考到牌出嚟個陣真係淨係望鏡唔望盲點<br />\n但有一次係青馬轉汀九個個位cut出去個陣望鏡冇車就出<br />\n點知係盲點到有架車呠我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚇到我即刻扭返入去<br />\n自始之後就次次都望盲點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638706baf337757adc73a05bd7b7a75582178697","tid":99342,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:46:38.000Z","msg":"如果你經常留意左右兩側路面 <br />\n其實好難唔知有車入左盲點"},{"pid":"7ce336e2a74fbfa02288542ebe12574250af0cd6","tid":99342,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:48:09.000Z","msg":"考果陣我擰頭純粹係做樣事實上係無望過<br />\n出黎渣過一排中過伏先識得望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28f7860ae5f526e4f1a19e149290e66b84953c6","tid":99342,"uid":26913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:51:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>考果陣我擰頭純粹係做樣事實上係無望過<br />\n出黎渣過一排中過伏先識得望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nX2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7c0b443e701190efb0e41d62d16a3579e2d475","tid":99342,"uid":13558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2014/07/22/a1124670.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fxtr%2Fb5%2F2014%2F07%2F22%2Fa1124670.html&d=OECIOtpIYN%2BcfPKO8P2P33vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=c15e8180\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2014/07/22/a1124670.html</a><br />\n<br />\n較好側鏡，shoulder check 都可以擰少啲同快啲。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁校法真係要d時間適應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但真係唔洗望咁耐"},{"pid":"fbc1d48821ddcdea9171a20b8bf8f5189bf2aef7","tid":99342,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:53:58.000Z","msg":"望盲點真係好緊要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f95078bd87cde4a8c0a4394a80123b8c5511c7","tid":99342,"uid":33826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:58:23.000Z","msg":"自從有次冇望差啲出事，從此我每次cut線一唔100%肯定安全都會睇盲區<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f1f8460b6855b0a773634368dde231c3d103d7","tid":99342,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:02:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自從有次冇望差啲出事，從此我每次cut線一唔100%肯定安全都會睇盲區<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都喺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果唔喺gps彈個error 出嚟我想噤走佢先再cut線, 應該炒左埋去部180up 嘅車度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (當時喺外國highway)"},{"pid":"b7ba4e73f06825f55e9c777446fd1611b7c88e00","tid":99342,"uid":38047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:05:54.000Z","msg":"上youtube打'唔望盲區'睇下啲片啦<br />\n你到而家都冇事唔係因為望盲區冇用，係你靠緊運氣支持你咋！"},{"pid":"a0cf0000f3474f7fead33da711c03b937b4fce8a","tid":99342,"uid":4032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:50:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2014/07/22/a1124670.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fxtr%2Fb5%2F2014%2F07%2F22%2Fa1124670.html&d=OECIOtpIYN%2BcfPKO8P2P33vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=c15e8180\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2014/07/22/a1124670.html</a><br />\n<br />\n較好側鏡，shoulder check 都可以擰少啲同快啲。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁校法真係要d時間適應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但真係唔洗望咁耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好易適應。你都唔會望到側鏡有嘢都夾硬cut 出去；加埋個擰少少嘅shoulder check，眼尾已經睇到隔離有無車。基本上唔會有啲你本來需要睇到嘅嘢而家睇唔到。"},{"pid":"5b16d372b8608b552c1e5e00c5356d10075cc999","tid":99342,"uid":59466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:31:30.000Z","msg":"行路都要望啦<br />\n何況係揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d615947a5bc1ecf7ec980804d6d271c52b0c06fe","tid":99342,"uid":49247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:36:31.000Z","msg":"揸26表示望多眼洗死咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好同我講明知係盲點你都唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b252e965b5ec93b9afea6423cb7eedbad773dd9a","tid":99342,"uid":15206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T10:20:39.000Z","msg":"學神果陣上左好多堂，由一開始為做而做學到明白望盲點既重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 救左我好多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470fe845d2060f7bef2557cf6767cbbe797349bc","tid":99342,"uid":20137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T10:28:05.000Z","msg":"公路匯合位/ 架車太斜出會有盲點 要望<br />\n泊係路邊成行死車要出車都會望"},{"pid":"95a9f3c46a983827c9442dfea11fc64b799537bc","tid":99342,"uid":30922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T10:30:04.000Z","msg":"有d位真係要擰轉頭望"},{"pid":"16c21c70e1181950ef922f8052e8cff4815c1e97","tid":99342,"uid":20137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T10:30:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揸26表示望多眼洗死咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好同我講明知係盲點你都唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多26渣到貼一貼又無啦啦標出黎 擰左頭都好難望到佢"},{"pid":"f2880db7474bfff52ca0f874b30b52aaa906e1ab","tid":99342,"uid":72477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T10:38:01.000Z","msg":"睇你前面有無車行緊<br />\n<br />\n有車而且近/多既，唔會望<br />\n因為望果下一慢再望返前面分分鐘會對到前車（in case 咁岩你望後面而前車收慢/cut線）<br />\n<br />\n一般望前鏡+側鏡無車就打燈<br />\n打完再邊望住側鏡邊cut線就得<br />\n<br />\n如果你架車唔係大車既更加無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6f44a3a752c10c4c3c5ba6debbb9329eabc165","tid":99342,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:38:14.000Z","msg":"試過有26係盲點區<br />\n差啲出事"},{"pid":"6af616e76c0b2bafbe3ee7dd3c1bf6be229e21d8","tid":99342,"uid":58006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:43:35.000Z","msg":"我都係差D出過事之後轉線都會慣左望一望<br />\n但係就無考車個陣咁誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1792a9636f50ee46a19ea4a37d4761ba713d89","tid":99342,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:47:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過有26係盲點區<br />\n差啲出事</blockquote><br />\n學車果陣都試過，差d 炒<br />\n<br />\n但出黎渣車之後坐過好多次人地車，冇一個會擰頭轉線<br />\n<br />\n係咪側鏡視野夠廣就得，見有d 鏡中有鏡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 倒後鏡係咪可有可冇，貨van 都睇唔到（假設俾貨遮住）"},{"pid":"2ac1c9a8ca77eb3f69b3e1728249c9c0af2c95d8","tid":99342,"uid":56511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:08:22.000Z","msg":"1000000%要望. 為你好咋樓主."},{"pid":"2de33be99c3edf16444f982fb612321ed900a270","tid":99342,"uid":41803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:11:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過有26係盲點區<br />\n差啲出事</blockquote><br />\n學車果陣都試過，差d 炒<br />\n<br />\n但出黎渣車之後坐過好多次人地車，冇一個會擰頭轉線<br />\n<br />\n係咪側鏡視野夠廣就得，見有d 鏡中有鏡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 倒後鏡係咪可有可冇，貨van 都睇唔到（假設俾貨遮住）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n視野無可能廣到完全無盲點，一定要望。唔望等於搏一鋪，搏贏賺一秒，輸左可能一世唔安樂+"},{"pid":"1b51bba7fbcaea0790d0b204f6d41c5028faa5cb","tid":99342,"uid":42434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:15:20.000Z","msg":"每次都必睇<br />\n一黎好有用<br />\n二黎有意外大家都唔想 無謂懶個少少"},{"pid":"9fddccec65a5948d690130ebf71c7184463976d6","tid":99342,"uid":69928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:29:52.000Z","msg":"學車時試過無望盲點，差d收左架26皮，以後唔咁唔睇<br />\n仲有，其實公路匯合處都一定要睇，我試過到匯合點前一直有睇鏡，準備出時望盲點，先發現原來有架的士9同我平排，之後我收慢d佢又收慢，擺明想陰我！"},{"pid":"d4026dc29ab77d313a320029356cea9ddbfe0a7a","tid":99342,"uid":38930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學車時試過無望盲點，差d收左架26皮，以後唔咁唔睇<br />\n仲有，其實公路匯合處都一定要睇，我試過到匯合點前一直有睇鏡，準備出時望盲點，先發現原來有架的士9同我平排，之後我收慢d佢又收慢，擺明想陰我！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今日都試過<br />\n行緊中線要準備cut左落分叉路 有架綠的係我左8點方向，我打晒燈兼收慢比佢過，屌佢又跟住收慢，本身以為佢係好心想收慢比我入，點撚知同我同一速度到就到分隔雙白再加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  條好樣擺明見我P想陰我"},{"pid":"b1b0d5611974cb846567603b8bc05e365e4d504e","tid":99342,"uid":3930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T22:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>考果陣我擰頭純粹係做樣事實上係無望過<br />\n出黎渣過一排中過伏先識得望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nX2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n相信成N個人試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以後都望盲點<br />\n未試過俾乘客笑柒<br />\n就算笑咪笑，安全至上，平安番到屋企就我贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655a3b1f7f57d2ebc20642e53ab660aaa23c7372","tid":99342,"uid":49344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:20:01.000Z","msg":"揸電單車真係多得個班唔擰頭撚唔少<br />\n<br />\n尤其啲 dc9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc0e663c7f6782dbeed234a6abb247403106880","tid":99342,"uid":9540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:59:42.000Z","msg":"要特別小心:<br />\n1. 慢線入中線，有機會同時有車右線入中線<br />\n2. 路口入高速公路，唔熟悉路面狀況<br />\n<br />\n不過其實多數都望，揸得多就知係幾大機會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0967f460de04b890b03c7785aba82c6562cd802f","tid":99342,"uid":9540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T04:01:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過有26係盲點區<br />\n差啲出事</blockquote><br />\n學車果陣都試過，差d 炒<br />\n<br />\n但出黎渣車之後坐過好多次人地車，冇一個會擰頭轉線<br />\n<br />\n係咪側鏡視野夠廣就得，見有d 鏡中有鏡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 倒後鏡係咪可有可冇，貨van 都睇唔到（假設俾貨遮住）</blockquote><br />\n睇得多倒後鏡會知後左右有咩車/發生緊咩事<br />\n有突發情況都安全啲"},{"pid":"22633c96a5459c2ee0218c09819bf0ed0d6ec0d1","tid":99342,"uid":26353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:17:17.000Z","msg":"盲點真係有<br />\n唔係呃你<br />\n成架5座sedan咁大架喺鏡睇唔到<br />\n臨cut 先睇到佢篤油上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60968f505e9389085afe7b3dcfbcc24cf8151c5d","tid":99342,"uid":36583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:21:10.000Z","msg":"Shoulder check 已經成為自然反應 打燈擰頭轉線一秒內完成 諗唔到有咩原因唔做"},{"pid":"fc7424f68330503041f85a6decb4e2f6a1379c96","tid":99342,"uid":52656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:58:16.000Z","msg":"其實基本上都唔洗點睇(如果路係冇咩死車同盲點)<br />\n最緊要係睇撚住D 26 ZIP<br />\n同埋得閒睇下後鏡有冇D來勢凶凶同D 仆街26<br />\n仆街有次我行右線<br />\n無啦啦係我右邊ZIP出黎<br />\n載撚住條女<br />\n唔撚要命咁撚樣<br />\n都痴撚線"},{"pid":"5e4d8b6fe69138c2710518031bf58b3d9084ff33","tid":99342,"uid":37259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:14:38.000Z","msg":"早兩個月有日渣車<br />\n我行中線，我 fd 個架行慢線<br />\n有架 Prius 行快線，兩架係我前面左右平排咁行<br />\n之後兩架車一齊 cut 埋黎中線<br />\n電光火石間架 Prius 見到有車同時 cut 埋黎就去番自己線加速走人<br />\n我 fd 事後話完全唔知個陣有車 cut 埋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望一兩秒盲點呢 d 時間真係唔慳得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579ca2683dbfba5807f526fda64fb335dc8eecb4","tid":99342,"uid":76626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:30:18.000Z","msg":"試過屎忽痕有次係側鏡望唔到有車，再望盲點，原來人地架26係我後左門，好在無諗過cut線，否則就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb35dc2e9d22bb62e08e93d11dbe674363582c01","tid":99342,"uid":7291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:24:02.000Z","msg":"貼個圓鏡仔 係側鏡 咪得<br />\n無shoulder check過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d249c85b8608af3474ab03c27457524c4c8e6e6","tid":99342,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:28:13.000Z","msg":"係望完前面冇危險先望盲點架嘛<br />\n嗰下一秒多啲<br />\n點樣危險"},{"pid":"8766ad129e93ecce5ae26244f54373c066c0e5ae","tid":99342,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:28:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱考到牌出嚟個陣真係淨係望鏡唔望盲點<br />\n但有一次係青馬轉汀九個個位cut出去個陣望鏡冇車就出<br />\n點知係盲點到有架車呠我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚇到我即刻扭返入去<br />\n自始之後就次次都望盲點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw，自此"},{"pid":"ef4b991dafefe0b82a72e18a3215ff150894a51f","tid":99342,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:30:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>考果陣我擰頭純粹係做樣事實上係無望過<br />\n出黎渣過一排中過伏先識得望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起碼識改<br />\n<br />\n好多人以為考試嗰啲就係多鳩餘<br />\n自己唔識思考咁<br />\n人講乜佢就跟人講<br />\n盲點會因為唔係考試就唔存在架咩"},{"pid":"748f96b4241ee3a6c5ab6e73c3df2ba6be42c276","tid":99342,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:37:38.000Z","msg":"望到無車就要望返前面<br />\n<br />\n轉右線淨係望右邊有無車<br />\n<br />\n有車繼續望住右邊<br />\n<br />\n望到無為止<br />\n<br />\n咁揸法實危險啦<br />\n<br />\n望到無就轉<br />\n<br />\n望到有就望返前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45be1079321617a3bfc7c1d0f4631c65e0f28db","tid":99342,"uid":75765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T06:54:48.000Z","msg":"話明盲點， 除非你塊哈哈鏡睇晒超過90度， &hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"10ca2eaff5779d8136b4c16b6c1339f8acc21441","tid":99342,"uid":30644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T08:12:18.000Z","msg":"考18,19牌唔洗望，點睇？"},{"pid":"d9bb7f79d94a8e359553bdffee1ce5b86564296f","tid":99342,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T08:26:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>望到無車就要望返前面<br />\n<br />\n轉右線淨係望右邊有無車<br />\n<br />\n有車繼續望住右邊<br />\n<br />\n望到無為止<br />\n<br />\n咁揸法實危險啦<br />\n<br />\n望到無就轉<br />\n<br />\n望到有就望返前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會有人望到無車先望返前面架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩命"},{"pid":"55399999dc06e74c39fc0233d33cbc3c274ec5cb","tid":99342,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:06:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>學車時試過無望盲點，差d收左架26皮，以後唔咁唔睇<br />\n仲有，其實公路匯合處都一定要睇，我試過到匯合點前一直有睇鏡，準備出時望盲點，先發現原來有架的士9同我平排，之後我收慢d佢又收慢，擺明想陰我！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今日都試過<br />\n行緊中線要準備cut左落分叉路 有架綠的係我左8點方向，我打晒燈兼收慢比佢過，屌佢又跟住收慢，本身以為佢係好心想收慢比我入，點撚知同我同一速度到就到分隔雙白再加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  條好樣擺明見我P想陰我</blockquote><br />\n我甩左p好耐都試過<br />\n可能佢地當正呢d係收派彩好機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e540303876e51d83615816aab9a399d85b0d31","tid":99342,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:09:47.000Z","msg":"36 年駕駛經驗，一定要！"},{"pid":"8f2a50f1c7b5fcee934234a1c64f0bb330aef59e","tid":99342,"uid":13558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:18:49.000Z","msg":"我自己都堅持check盲點嘅，<br />\n見咁多巴打分享睇黎真係好緊要。<br />\n<br />\nbtw 揸車時候隔離位d乘客囉嗦真係好煩"},{"pid":"5d0674b957138594d4e9b362fab6872ceb64141e","tid":99342,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:32:58.000Z","msg":"我都試過差啲出事<br />\n唔好搏啦<br />\n大家揸車小心啦"},{"pid":"a7bf44e09033950da2a9f0e26c74a16e6777ce07","tid":99342,"uid":20137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:37:01.000Z","msg":"我考完牌渣車先知咩叫望盲點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n考果陣真係為擰而擰"},{"pid":"205e588414e1cf72c078c3af6d77240dde809497","tid":99342,"uid":53350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:43:24.000Z","msg":"落老龍d 交匯處唔望真係玩命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d6e780df69061f02a96a99c6ed54d2debc2c8c","tid":99342,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:10:52.000Z","msg":"其實又唔係咩位都要望盲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如,學車過死車返入自己條線果下要望盲<br />\n實際上邊有白痴仔會係人地過緊死車果陣,係中間插過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為其實無論司機望唔望到有電單車係果到插出嚟都好,架電單車咁行其實一定會炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於cut線,又真係無乜必要睇盲點<br />\n只要有良好習慣行緊直路都經常望鏡掌握附近有咩車<br />\n根本一早你就知隔離線有架車上嚟,係中鏡消失左,側鏡未見到,咪即係盲點有車囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋,cut線我真係建議自己俾油加速,然後先cut線,cut完再維持一小段高速先慢慢降速<br />\n咁做既可以令cut線難度降低,做一做個變速又可以確保你無睇漏任何野<br />\n<br />\n真係要望嘅位,我淨係數到自己小路出大路,入高速等等<br />\n只要自己係讓線出都一定要望盲點<br />\n因為通常呢d位你塊鏡根本望唔到主線<br />\n果個瞬間所有倒後鏡都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b5dee702cf7bf80c58157deeb2204b28273e04","tid":99342,"uid":16873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:37:56.000Z","msg":"揸26慣左成日望鏡，要養成習慣隨時留意身邊有無車，有無車要上黎心入面都有個譜"},{"pid":"eec4556c156ae939dccd7f457c1bdfd925ba318f","tid":99342,"uid":16471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T19:44:30.000Z","msg":"而家點都望左先 又唔會蝕既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494b9dd274d29f952bd6065e236d517c4097de1b","tid":99342,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:12:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8c75e1eb1279f1a5b6c034c2f0fa8f28dd67d4c","tid":99342,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:13:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11d53705fae5b207f11407822a568e5edf2aa329","tid":99342,"uid":30208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:32:39.000Z","msg":"p牌仔，試過早兩個月揸部Hiace 係清水灣出來， 望到左鏡冇車諗住cut 左， 一打燈cut 少少有車呠到仆街，我即刻扭返埋自己線， 原來有部transporter 係盲點， 佢過左我之後啤到我行一行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02632c8257f1461750c448a34e91b84c9ccf1d42","tid":99342,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:55:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>p牌仔，試過早兩個月揸部Hiace 係清水灣出來， 望到左鏡冇車諗住cut 左， 一打燈cut 少少有車呠到仆街，我即刻扭返埋自己線， 原來有部transporter 係盲點， 佢過左我之後啤到我行一行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所謂你班仆街炸彈，成撚日唔望就cut ，無事係你行緊運咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113e51af6834308912cfc202811ed486f26bc977","tid":99342,"uid":71075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:58:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de5d6f11de8b0cd8848ce0790515ebf633220215","tid":99342,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:26:00.000Z","msg":"小路上公路(斜斜地匯入)果啲一定睇<br />\n試過鏡睇唔到，但擰頭望見有大貨車衝緊嚟"},{"pid":"7c4b079b9cd2f414e427600eaa80ac362db13c6c","tid":99342,"uid":36583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:45:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實又唔係咩位都要望盲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如,學車過死車返入自己條線果下要望盲<br />\n實際上邊有白痴仔會係人地過緊死車果陣,係中間插過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為其實無論司機望唔望到有電單車係果到插出嚟都好,架電單車咁行其實一定會炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於cut線,又真係無乜必要睇盲點<br />\n只要有良好習慣行緊直路都經常望鏡掌握附近有咩車<br />\n根本一早你就知隔離線有架車上嚟,係中鏡消失左,側鏡未見到,咪即係盲點有車囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋,cut線我真係建議自己俾油加速,然後先cut線,cut完再維持一小段高速先慢慢降速<br />\n咁做既可以令cut線難度降低,做一做個變速又可以確保你無睇漏任何野<br />\n<br />\n真係要望嘅位,我淨係數到自己小路出大路,入高速等等<br />\n只要自己係讓線出都一定要望盲點<br />\n因為通常呢d位你塊鏡根本望唔到主線<br />\n果個瞬間所有倒後鏡都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n祝你好運 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7d9b1588a9a53e8c31bf3fbc85cd610e037f83","tid":99342,"uid":31809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T09:55:40.000Z","msg":"親身經驗!! 絕對有需要望盲點!!<br />\n由其係以下2個條件：<br />\n1. 夜晚<br />\n2. 對方架車係黑色<br />\n<br />\n當對方入左你左或右盲區，你望任何鏡都唔會睇到佢<br />\n而因為黑色車你眼尾係唔會覺有車係你隔離<br />\n直至你 shoulder check 先會驚覺有架車係隔離!!<br />\n<br />\n所以各位巴絲打為安全著想，一定要 shoulder check 望左盲區先好 cut!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15aa8c5fb80eedaae83ff40e80950d9b9b13d3fb","tid":99342,"uid":30208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:40:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>p牌仔，試過早兩個月揸部Hiace 係清水灣出來， 望到左鏡冇車諗住cut 左， 一打燈cut 少少有車呠到仆街，我即刻扭返埋自己線， 原來有部transporter 係盲點， 佢過左我之後啤到我行一行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所謂你班仆街炸彈，成撚日唔望就cut ，無事係你行緊運咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以後會望清楚喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80d944611bce274bda9f44f394e5c716ec5be9b","tid":99342,"uid":10743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:51:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實又唔係咩位都要望盲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如,學車過死車返入自己條線果下要望盲<br />\n實際上邊有白痴仔會係人地過緊死車果陣,係中間插過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為其實無論司機望唔望到有電單車係果到插出嚟都好,架電單車咁行其實一定會炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於cut線,又真係無乜必要睇盲點<br />\n只要有良好習慣行緊直路都經常望鏡掌握附近有咩車<br />\n根本一早你就知隔離線有架車上嚟,係中鏡消失左,側鏡未見到,咪即係盲點有車囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋,cut線我真係建議自己俾油加速,然後先cut線,cut完再維持一小段高速先慢慢降速<br />\n咁做既可以令cut線難度降低,做一做個變速又可以確保你無睇漏任何野<br />\n<br />\n真係要望嘅位,我淨係數到自己小路出大路,入高速等等<br />\n只要自己係讓線出都一定要望盲點<br />\n因為通常呢d位你塊鏡根本望唔到主線<br />\n果個瞬間所有倒後鏡都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n解釋得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我平時都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e615daa31b3484315467806caf11c913740ee9d9","tid":99342,"uid":72735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:28:31.000Z","msg":"一定望<br />\n睇得太多YouTube盲毛片<br />\n唔想無啦啦撞死人<br />\n<br />\n上面有巴打話咩一直留路面情況唔洗望<br />\n我就唔同意<br />\n揸車切忌以為自己掌握一切<br />\n路面秒秒鐘變化，你真係可以肯定永遠咁專注？<br />\n可能你傾一句計，聽一句收音機，甚至咁啱諗緊野，已經睇漏左<br />\n你睇一個盲點分分鐘救人一命<br />\n點解唔做足？"},{"pid":"6abaaa212a82c48fb0114e754c87f74eb20fd494","tid":99342,"uid":8549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:01:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自從有次冇望差啲出事，從此我每次cut線一唔100%肯定安全都會睇盲區<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648399a7282fbd76794210f0440d9405e50bd1d8","tid":99342,"uid":8549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上youtube打'唔望盲區'睇下啲片啦<br />\n你到而家都冇事唔係因為望盲區冇用，係你靠緊運氣支持你咋！</blockquote><br />\n冇錯，唔望肓點真係好易累死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5c4fd44c05020499a80dcadcfe9b10623807b9","tid":99342,"uid":8549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:06:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揸26表示望多眼洗死咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好同我講明知係盲點你都唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有次望少一次，差啲抄低隔離架26，自此以後一定定做足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}